description:
A classic Jamaican movie from 1978 about some rastafarians struggling with their daily lives in Kingston&amp;#039;s slum areas, playing reggae, earning money and robbing the mafia in a Robin Hood kind of way. :) Virtually the entire cast is comprised of Jamaica&amp;#039;s leading reggae musicians.
